Father.

4
00:00:19,500 --> 00:00:20,890
The one who hijacked the execution ground

5
00:00:21,320 --> 00:00:22,519
may not be Xuanyi.

6
00:00:25,199 --> 00:00:26,239
Besides him,

7
00:00:26,559 --> 00:00:28,199
who else has the courage?

8
00:00:28,640 --> 00:00:29,399
Moreover,

9
00:00:29,679 --> 00:00:31,559
have you seen him until now?

10
00:00:32,079 --> 00:00:33,399
This witch.

11
00:00:33,840 --> 00:00:35,719
Was it not enough to kill Qing'an?

12
00:00:40,000 --> 00:00:41,090
Please show mercy, Your Majesty.

13
00:00:41,280 --> 00:00:43,479
Xuanyi must have been bewitched
by that witch.

14
00:00:43,600 --> 00:00:44,920
Please spare him.

15
00:00:45,100 --> 00:00:45,990
Princess Dowager Yuan.

16
00:00:46,000 --> 00:00:46,799
Get up quickly.

17
00:00:47,240 --> 00:00:47,759
Help her up.

18
00:00:48,000 --> 00:00:48,759
Your Highness.

19
00:00:48,840 --> 00:00:49,600
Get up.

20
00:00:51,100 --> 00:00:51,990
Princess Dowager Yuan.

21
00:00:52,119 --> 00:00:53,799
This matter shouldn't be made public.

22
00:00:54,079 --> 00:00:54,840
Now,

23
00:00:55,000 --> 00:00:56,439
we must first find them.

24
00:01:02,000 --> 00:01:03,159
I remember last time,

25
00:01:04,000 --> 00:01:05,550
you helped me
apply the medicine like this too.

26
00:01:07,000 --> 00:01:07,799
It's a pity.

27
00:01:08,760 --> 00:01:09,560
Pity?

28
00:01:10,599 --> 00:01:11,799
It's a pity

29
