38
00:01:45,159 --> 00:01:46,319
Fool.

39
00:01:49,359 --> 00:01:50,680
I want to go back.

40
00:01:51,439 --> 00:01:52,760
I don't want to live with shackles

41
00:01:52,760 --> 00:01:53,799
in this world.

42
00:01:54,799 --> 00:01:56,159
I don't want my child

43
00:01:56,359 --> 00:01:58,000
to have a mother who is a murderer.

44
00:01:59,000 --> 00:02:00,480
If I leave now,

45
00:02:00,599 --> 00:02:02,480
