who killed Tang Yin'er.

51
00:02:18,360 --> 00:02:19,840
Well, Tang Wanwan.

52
00:02:20,080 --> 00:02:21,240
You committed murder

53
00:02:21,420 --> 00:02:22,919
and escaped from the execution ground.

54
00:02:23,319 --> 00:02:24,199
Each of these

55
00:02:24,280 --> 00:02:26,879
is enough for you
to lose your head 100 times over.

56
00:02:27,520 --> 00:02:28,199
Now,

57
00:02:28,400 --> 00:02:30,120
