to negotiate terms with me?

58
00:02:31,960 --> 00:02:33,400
Since I've chosen to come back,

59
00:02:33,719 --> 00:02:35,120
I have nothing to fear.

60
00:02:36,050 --> 00:02:37,439
Your Majesty,
please judge wisely.

61
00:02:37,840 --> 00:02:39,560
Give me the chance to clear my name.

62
00:02:41,919 --> 00:02:43,199
What if, after half a month,

63
00:02:43,680 --> 00:02:45,000
