79
00:03:29,520 --> 00:03:30,599
How can that be?

80
00:03:31,120 --> 00:03:32,360
I can't go back on my words.

81
00:03:33,120 --> 00:03:34,280
I'll take

82
00:03:35,280 --> 00:03:35,919
