83
00:03:39,560 --> 00:03:40,560
No.

84
00:03:42,080 --> 00:03:42,879
It's okay.

85
00:03:43,159 --> 00:03:43,919
It doesn't hurt.

86
00:03:45,120 --> 00:03:47,360
