102
00:04:27,160 --> 00:04:28,160
I have nine lives.

103
00:04:28,279 --> 00:04:29,560
A tail serves as a life.

104
00:04:29,839 --> 00:04:31,040
I'm not afraid of you.

105
00:04:33,480 --> 00:04:34,439
